Quad-kiting in PoFire is HARD. While I'm a bit irate at the thought of someone racking up 75% of an AA per kite, I have to admit that any druid who does it has earned that exp. Out of wizards and druids combined, I'd be surprised if there's more than 10 people per server that can quad in PoFire.</p>
	
	
	
