On the druid thing:<br />
<br />
I've duo'd a lot in PoP...with druids.  Not just helping them charm-kite.  Many times (most times, in fact) I tanked, they healed.  Random desert creatures in Storms, razorfiends in Valor.  With a beastlord or better slower, a druid is Cleric Mark II.  There's very little Sony could give druids right now to improve group-desirability that wouldn't make them overpowerful; it's not about what druids can and can't do, it's about what dumbass_public04 thinks.</p>
	
	
	
