	<td class="alt2" width="175" align="center" valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><b>Elured</b>
<span class="smallfont">
	<br />
	Die, Die And Go To Hell<br />
		
	<br /><img src="image.php?s=7d1a18fd3354f531a38f4b8b8786d947&amp;userid=18940&amp;dateline=1043773681" border="0" alt="Avatar" title="Elured's Avatar" hspace="4" vspace="4" /><br />
